questions.name: Q-1
questions.question_usr: Q: Generate an esoteric french phrase. (Then explain why it would be considered esoteric) A:
questions.completion:
"Les étoiles dansent avec les murmures du vent"

This phrase could be considered esoteric because it combines elements of nature (stars and wind) with a sense of mysticism and poetic imagery. It conveys a sense of interconnectedness between the celestial and earthly realms, which may not be easily understood or appreciated by everyone. Additionally, the use of poetic language and metaphor adds to the esoteric nature of the phrase.
